--- Richard Allen <roborick007@...> wrote:

> ::Lord Jhiaxus::
> 
> Jhiaxus squares up the new bot who is with Hydras.
> 
> Jhiaxus: Welcome to the Predacons. I'm new here as well.

Myrmidon's tall broad form stepped into the room, his movements
graceful and yet powerful. He glanced at Jhiaxus and then swept the
room as if studying it for traps, or prey. Finally Myrmidon's purple
optics fixed on Jhiaxus, glowing from beneath his lion-like helm. He
nodded, "Greetings Jhiaxus." His deep voice easilly filling the room.
"What is this about revenge against Rodimus Prime, and plans to rescue
Hydras' captured subordinate?"

Preston
(Myrmidon)
